snippet.title: Stray Cat Crossing Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
Check us out on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/385330/

Stray Cat Crossing is an indie pixel horror game developed in RPG Maker.
Download the free demo here: http://rpgmaker.net/games/6962/downloads/

Song: Skintight
Music by Jurlo
Vocals by Sara Lu: http://instantromanticism.tumblr.com

Want more? Visit our Devblog! http://straycatcrossing.tumblr.com
